**`tokio/src/runtime/scheduler/inject.rs`**

`inject::Shared<Arc<Handle>>` is a multi-producer intrusive linked list protected by the scheduler mutex (`Synced`). `push()` and `pop_n()` both acquire `shared.synced.lock()`. Used for:
